hopobject.body: Lost credit card cara beli cytotec tanpa resep dokter He added: "It works for very large firms because they can get economies of scale. They have got whole teams of people living out there who are embedded in the contact centres. But an SME can't afford to do that so they do a halfway house and get 30 people working out of some offshore contact centre. As a result they usually get poor customer service, terrible staff attrition and it just doesn't really work. They should be focused on keep their customers and creating exceptional customer service back here in the UK."
